nodes.text: Star Wars: OBI-123 is a Star Wars young readers book written by Calliope Glass and Caitlin Kennedy. Illustrated by Katie Cook and released on February 14, 2017, the title is a follow-up to Star Wars: ABC-3PO.

ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR
Counting with Star Wars is hardly a chore!
From the chosen ONE to a transport of TWENTY
This book is full of numbers aplenty!
So, Padawans, prepare, get ready, get set
For a numerical lesson you'll never forget!
